National_City.Bayside at the Embarcadero: Bayside at the Embarcadero is the 14th tallest building in San Diego, California and is a prominent fixture in San Diego's skyline. It has a height of 395 ft (120 m) and 232 units. Located in the Core district of Downtown San Diego, Bayside is a 36-story building that utilizes the postmodern architectural style and was designed by the architect firm Amanat Architect.
